    "faq_aUggGR": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "text_AbCdEf": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How long does it take for delivery after I place my order?",
            "answer": "<p>US orders are dispatched through our US warehouse using USPS express delivery services with tracked delivery in 3-5 days.</p><p>Other international orders are dispatched using DHL Express, who offer worldwide fully tracked delivery in 4-7 business days.</p><p>Please note: Any import duties or taxes, which are levied by the authorities of your country once the product reaches your country, are at your cost.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_GhIjKl": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you ship overseas?",
            "answer": "<p>Absolutely! We ship to many international destinations. To check if we ship to your country, please put an item(s) in your shopping cart and proceed to checkout, where you will be able to select the shipping destination from the list of countries. If we are unable to ship to your country, it will show as ‘no shipping options available’.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_MnOpQr": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What happens if my parcel doesn’t arrive by the expected time?",
            "answer": "<p>For expected delivery times please visit our shipping page. Please note that these are estimated time frames, not guaranteed. There can occasionally be delays when orders enter the receiving country which are out of our control. If you have not received your parcel within a reasonable timeframe, please contact us at support@medicinalmadhoney.com along with your order details, and we will investigate it for you.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_StUvWx": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Will customs let my parcel through?",
            "answer": "<p>Customs and import regulations vary widely between countries. Some of the products we sell via this website are prohibited from importation into certain countries. Unfortunately, it is not possible for us to be aware of all the regulations specific to each country that we ship to. We do, however, try to highlight any import restrictions via the ‘shipping’ page.</p><p>Any import duties or taxes, which are levied by the authorities of your country once the product reaches your country, are at your cost. Medicinal Mad Honey accepts no liability for the refund/replacement of any goods or any costs relating to, or arising from, the importation or confiscation of any goods by your country's Customs Office or other government body.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_YzAbCd": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How can I return an item?",
            "answer": "<p>Please contact us at support@medicinalmadhoney.com to discuss this. Return costs must be covered by the customer.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_EfGhIj": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "The product I received is damaged. What do I do now?",
            "answer": "<p>Please contact us with your issue as soon as you receive the order so that we can resolve it for you as soon as possible. Please ensure that you send us a photo of the damaged item(s), the batch number, and your order number. This information is required for us to raise an investigation with our shipping provider and to ensure that this will not happen again.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_KlMnOp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I cancel my order?",
            "answer": "<p>If for some reason you need to cancel your order, please call us as soon as possible and provide us with your order number. Please note that we are unable to cancel orders that have already been dispatched.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_QrStUv": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What forms of payment do you accept?",
            "answer": "<p>We currently accept Paypal, Visa, and Mastercard payments. We offer a secure payment system to give our customers peace of mind. None of our customers' credit card information is stored.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_WxYzAb": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How much is shipping?",
            "answer": "<p>We offer free shipping within Nepal on all orders.</p><p>For international orders, the cost of shipping depends on the weight of the order and is calculated at the checkout page. To find out more about our shipping terms and conditions, please visit our shipping page.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_CdEfGh": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I track my order?",
            "answer": "<p>Once you place an order with us, you will receive tracking email updates as soon as your parcel gets scanned in by your shipping carrier and a tracking number to easily follow the journey of your package. You can easily track your order through our portal here.</p><p>If you have any questions or concerns about your order, don’t hesitate to reach out at support@medicinalmadhoney.com. We will always solve any shipping/delivery issues you may have.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
