    "faq_z3PHy9": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "text_QrStUv": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Are your lip balms all natural?",
            "answer": "<p>All our products contain natural ingredients, sourced from hills and mountains of Nepal. We do, however, promise that our products are created with all-natural, mad wild honey bee-sourced ingredients sustainably derived from the <a href=\"/pages/honey-hunter\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Honey Hunters\">honey hunters of Nepal</a>.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_WxYzAb": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Where are your lip balms manufactured?",
            "answer": "<p><a href=\"/collections/all\" title=\"All\">All of our products</a> are manufactured in Nepal, through our in-house team.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_CdEfGh": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I use Mad Honey lip balm as a base before applying lipstick or other lip products?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, you definitely can! Most of our customers use Honeybalm combined with their lipstick or lip gloss, but you can also apply it without any other lip cosmetics. You can even use Honey Balm as an overnight lip mask!</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_IjKlMn": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What are the benefits of Mad Honey lip balm?",
            "answer": "<p>Normal and ordinary lip balms are made with a lot of chemicals that are bad for your lips. Our wild honey balm is made with real, organic ingredients such as mad honey bee wax and propolis. This gives your lips a hydrating and protective base, straight from mother nature. <a href=\"/products/lip-balm\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Mad Honey Lip Balm\">Wild mad honey lip balms </a>keep your lips soft, hydrated, protected, and beautiful.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_OpQrSt": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What ingredients are used in the madhoney lip balms?",
            "answer": "<p>All of our lip balms are made with real, organic ingredients. Please check our ingredients page for all the ingredients we use for each flavor.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
